{"tid":13702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇維埃紀念塔上怎麼有隻派大星　俄羅斯警方怒","createTime":"2016-11-30T07:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T08:38:02.000Z","uid":43468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3567799db36b9a4638ad22a97fca8d3a3b33f257","tid":13702,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:43:33.000Z","msg":"觀光客到俄羅斯常常造訪的著名景點蘇維埃紀念塔，近日居然被街頭藝術家惡搞了一番。蘇維埃紀念塔上的星星標誌，竟然被塗成了卡通海綿寶寶中的角色「派大星」。<br />\n<br />\n於是俄羅斯沃羅涅日市的警方憤怒急著想要逮人，揪出到底是誰這麼膽大包天，竟敢惡搞著名地標。警方表示，清理星星標誌上的派大星費用高達1500美金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgapi.nownews.com/?w=640&amp;q=75&amp;src=http://s.nownews.com/media_crop/151896/hash/6f/6c/6f6c47ec3aa629a6534f5ee303551b1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgapi.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D640%26q%3D75%26src%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fs.nownews.com%2Fmedia_crop%2F151896%2Fhash%2F6f%2F6c%2F6f6c47ec3aa629a6534f5ee303551b1e.jpg&h=64a41641&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41eeb2cb3b58e90eda99511e77aa5c920d6743ba","tid":13702,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>觀光客到俄羅斯常常造訪的著名景點蘇維埃紀念塔，近日居然被街頭藝術家惡搞了一番。蘇維埃紀念塔上的星星標誌，竟然被塗成了卡通海綿寶寶中的角色「派大星」。<br />\n<br />\n於是俄羅斯沃羅涅日市的警方憤怒急著想要逮人，揪出到底是誰這麼膽大包天，竟敢惡搞著名地標。警方表示，清理星星標誌上的派大星費用高達1500美金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgapi.nownews.com/?w=640&amp;q=75&amp;src=http://s.nownews.com/media_crop/151896/hash/6f/6c/6f6c47ec3aa629a6534f5ee303551b1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgapi.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D640%26q%3D75%26src%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fs.nownews.com%2Fmedia_crop%2F151896%2Fhash%2F6f%2F6c%2F6f6c47ec3aa629a6534f5ee303551b1e.jpg&h=61822584&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/taoeq4j0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftaoeq4j0&h=69b4a50a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ccdd996cd99aa536fe8fe1e3468b76ef51c1284","tid":13702,"uid":27575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T